ctable normalizing constants. Our analysis results show strong\nspatial associations between teeth and tooth surfaces and that dental hygienic\nfactors, fluorosis and sealant reduce the risks of having dental diseases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2018 00:18:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2018 20:39:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2019 10:26:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-15"}
