aracteristics of both the first order and the second order\ntopological insulators, simultaneously, which is consistent with the recent\nclassification of higher-order topological insulators protected by an order-two\nsymmetry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2018 05:30:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Oct 2018 07:18:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2019 14:37:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
